{"tid":198714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果宜家嘅中國好似","createTime":"2017-04-12T16:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T17:56:49.000Z","uid":42602,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97164268768d1549e0964763954da868271581e4","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:49:21.000Z","msg":"唐朝咁盛世<br />\n漢宋朝咁強大<br />\n啲人民又唔係經歷過文革咁咁痴線<br />\n<br />\n你仲認唔認自己做中國人？<br />\n<br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c0a4a0690b7799af16db09681aeccee47a1e9c","tid":198714,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"人民質素點先"},{"pid":"ca5b29914d379df80c3085703a9bc35293d2a0bb","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人民質素點先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難有個標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當係戰國啦好嗎 四大家好似都係嗰段時間發蹟"},{"pid":"824a9aa8282c0e3f94b0002aa0a61c27883d1be0","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"利個申先<br />\n啲歷史嘢錯嘅勿屌<br />\n小弟我理科仔"},{"pid":"f36e180e8270efff6a8e04246dc329b7fd9fef4a","tid":198714,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人民質素點先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難有個標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當係戰國啦好嗎 四大家好似都係嗰段時間發蹟</blockquote><br />\n我自己就會如果人民質素同知識水平高、有修養嘅話<br />\n國力強唔強我都會認自己係中國人"},{"pid":"53444c4fb275dc34dcc7e34c9545e789b7ec77e0","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人民質素點先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難有個標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當係戰國啦好嗎 四大家好似都係嗰段時間發蹟</blockquote><br />\n我自己就會如果人民質素同知識水平高、有修養嘅話<br />\n國力強唔強我都會認自己係中國人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣好睇人民質素<br />\n唔係唔想認自己係點中國人<br />\n係唔想同嗰班友一樣俾人叫做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8858503197104cd80a287ea4a46b77ec16e26d4","tid":198714,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"點成日問人認唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb947418228cf9cd0e8f2b94a3b8758c7514a859","tid":198714,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:24:19.000Z","msg":"唔係認唔認 而係根本唔係<br />\n而且中國侵略香港係唔會改變"},{"pid":"53c666e4ae7b0173c911e0b09b682b6bf43048c6","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點成日問人認唔認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n純粹問下如果個身份真係會令你自豪嘅話你會唔會承認呢個身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真我都唔明點解要係用國家嚟分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話大又唔夠大話細又唔細"},{"pid":"f84b2b0d46558a792f6d882f4a16ae1868400b1b","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係認唔認 而係根本唔係<br />\n而且中國侵略香港係唔會改變</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每一個國家都係靠侵略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2385a33b4d40664ac1f3902cfba158b91a8db7fe","tid":198714,"uid":15588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係認唔認 而係根本唔係<br />\n而且中國侵略香港係唔會改變</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每一個國家都係靠侵略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搶完咪話係自己既土地，講講下其實每一個國家都係搶匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c605c48172ca13bf127469e3b0d9f8b7f0b08b01","tid":198714,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係認唔認 而係根本唔係<br />\n而且中國侵略香港係唔會改變</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每一個國家都係靠侵略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搶完咪話係自己既土地，講講下其實每一個國家都係搶匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勝者為王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}